defaultAs members of the
default UK End Violence Against Women Coalition (EVAW) AI supports EVAW’s call for a Prevention Plan to set out action to change harmful attitudes and behaviours in order to save lives and reduce the emotional, physical and financial cost of violence in the long term.  
